{"tid":888194,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"箍牙撚齊來叫春+答我問題","createTime":"2018-11-03T14:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T14:08:31.000Z","uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9edc1f656427817129af90d0728724a8c91b7cb","tid":888194,"uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我終於拆左傳統鐵箍 <br />\n依架開始帶透明固定器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條利忍唔住成日奶舊野 <br />\n介損左利底生左粒飛滋<br />\n依架吞啖口水都痛到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講野又癡唒利根<br />\n已經唔想開聲同人講野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪因爲啲牙移位<br />\n痛到個人都無心機做野 <br />\n剩係想訓係床休息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n用手同利奶隻牙個陣<br />\n硬係覺得上排有隻牙凹咗少少 <br />\n(箍牙前個隻牙係凹入去） <br />\n但個固定器帶得落姐係證明隻牙無凹落去咁誇張？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日好驚啲牙移位 <br />\n其實係咪就算移左少少 <br />\n塞得落個固定器都可以拉翻齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想快啲過左三個月 <br />\n然後剩係夜晚帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}